        <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:.4rem">TOP FINDING</div>
        <div style="font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.65;color:var(--text2)"><strong style="color:var(--text)">English speakers generalize 2.6× more</strong> than German speakers. hasty_generalization at 68% EN vs. 26% DE. Cultural argumentation difference, not language.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:14px;padding:1rem">
        <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--green);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:.4rem">BIGGEST IMPROVEMENT</div>
        <div style="font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.65;color:var(--text2)"><strong style="color:var(--text)">IntuitionTranslator</strong> found hidden strong insights in 19 of 150 arguments (13%). People with the right idea but wrong framing now get shown the academic version of their own thought.</div>
      </div>
